# Installation

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/syswatch.git
cd syswatch

Make scripts executable:

chmod +x syswatch
chmod +x modules/*.sh
chmod +x core/*.sh
Usage

Run full scan:

./syswatch run

Run live monitoring:

./syswatch live

Build file integrity baseline:

./syswatch integrity-baseline

Check file integrity:

./syswatch integrity-check
